import './App.css';
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';
import Articles from './data.js';

import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row';
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card';

import { Button, Nav, Navbar } from 'react-bootstrap';



function App() {
  const art_i = 0
  return (

    <Container className='p-0 App vh-100' fluid>

      <Navbar bg="light p-3" data-bs-theme="light">
        <Container fluid >
          <Navbar.Brand className='fs-1' href="#home">NEWSBOARD</Navbar.Brand>
          <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
          <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
            <Nav className="me-auto">
              <Nav.Link className='fs-5' href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
              <Nav.Link className='fs-5' href="#link">Link</Nav.Link>
            </Nav>
          </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Container>
      </Navbar>

      <Container className='d-flex align-items-stretch App h-75' fluid>


        <Col >

          <Row className="h-75">

            <Col md={3}>
              <Card variant="light">
                <Card.Img variant="top" src={Articles[art_i].img} />
                <Card.Body>
                  <Card.Title className='fs-3' >{Articles[art_i].title}</Card.Title>
                  <Card.Text className='crop-text-2' >
                    {Articles[art_i].description}
                  </Card.Text>
                </Card.Body>
              </Card>
            </Col>

            <Col  md={2}>

               <Card variant="light" >
                <Card.Body>
                  <Card.Title>{Articles[art_i + 2].title}</Card.Title>
                  <Card.Text className='crop-text-2' >
                    {Articles[art_i + 2].description}
                  </Card.Text>
                </Card.Body>
              </Card>

              <Card variant="light" >
                <Card.Img variant="top" src={Articles[art_i + 1].img} />
                <Card.Body>
                  <Card.Title className='fs-3'>{Articles[art_i + 1].title}</Card.Title>
                </Card.Body>
              </Card>

             

            </Col>

            <Col md={2}>
              <Card variant="light">
                <Card.Img variant="top" src={Articles[art_i + 4].img} />
                <Card.Body>
                  <Card.Title>{Articles[art_i + 4].title}</Card.Title>
                  <Card.Text className='crop-text-2' >
                    {Articles[art_i + 4].description}
                  </Card.Text>
                </Card.Body>
              </Card>
            </Col>

          </Row>

        </Col>

      </Container>



    </Container >

  );
}

export default App;
